# Datasets ARE committed (data/) so the firewalled office machine can use the
# repo offline -- with one exception: the CIFAR-10 tarball exceeds GitHub's
# 100 MB file limit. Only the extracted cifar-10-batches-py/ is committed;
# torchvision verifies the extracted batch files and never needs the tarball.
data/cifar-10-python.tar.gz
